{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"伺服器","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Server","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>硬體而言的伺服器（server）是個能在網路上，提供用戶端服務的共享性電腦（shared computer）。軟體而言的伺服器程式，則是指能給用戶端提供服務的程式。</p>\n<p>服務（Services）通常會提供於內部網路、或是公開網路。用戶端程式與伺服器端程式通常利用 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Protocol\">protocol</a> 來傳送編碼的數據、並依此連接之。</p>\n<p>內部網路最常見的伺服器有檔案、域名、電郵、印表機、還有傳真伺服器。另一個常見的伺服器是連結到網際網路的 Web 伺服器。在資料中心（data center）的微電腦、大型電腦、還有超級電腦... 等，也都是伺服器。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"一般知識","title":"一般知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/What_is_a_web_server\">伺服器介紹</a></li>\n  <li>維基百科的<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%BC%BA%E6%9C%8D%E5%99%A8\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">伺服器</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"硬體而言的伺服器（server）是個能在網路上，提供用戶端服務的共享性電腦（shared computer）。軟體而言的伺服器程式，則是指能給用戶端提供服務的程式。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Server","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Serveur","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Server (サーバー)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Server","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Servidor","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Server","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"服务器","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/server","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/server/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary","title":"術語表"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Server","title":"伺服器"}],"pageTitle":"伺服器 - 術語表 | MDN","noIndex